ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 225, Quebec
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 225 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the Minister to provide financial assistance to the province of QUEBEC, with respect to the spring flooding that occurred from April 14 to June 7, 2019.
